% Test: Modulo with negative numbers
% Expected: Consistent modulo behavior
% Category: 15_arithmetic
% Priority: P2 - Arithmetic patterns

.kg create test_mod_neg
.kg use test_mod_neg

+numbers[(-7,), (-5,), (0,), (5,), (7,)].

